subject: Football (College)
Bowl Games
organizations: Rutgers, The State University of New Jersey
Virginia Polytechnic Institute and State University
lead_paragraph: Rutgers faltered after a promising start to the Russell Athletic Bowl on Friday, falling to Virginia Tech in overtime and ending its season with three straight losses.
